  </p>

  <div class="flex gap-4">
    <a href="/projects" class="px-6 py-3 bg-cyan-600 hover:bg-cyan-500 text-white rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors shadow-lg shadow-cyan-500/30">
      查看研究專案
